# DRAMPA Project Intelligence

## Design Patterns

### Color Scheme
- Primary brand color: #FF7722 (orange)
- Neutral background: white
- Light orange background: #FFF0E6
- Dark orange (hover): #E65100
- Text: Neutral/gray for body, primary color for headings

### Component Architecture
- UI components should be placed in src/components/ui/
- Section components should be placed in src/components/sections/
- MagicUI components should be adapted with orange theming

### Code Style Preferences
- Use functional components with hooks
- Arrow function syntax for component definitions
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- TypeScript interfaces for props
- JSDoc comments for component documentation

### Implementation Specifics
- For file uploads, use react-dropzone
- For animations, use framer-motion sparingly for performance
- Session storage is used for cross-page state persistence
- Prefer grid layout for responsive designs
- Use radial gradient masks for subtle visual effects

## User Workflow Preferences
- Focus on simplicity and clarity in UI
- Provide visual feedback during async operations (loading states)
- Ensure mobile responsiveness for all components
- Use orange buttons for primary actions
- Use outlined/light buttons for secondary actions

## Current Development Focus
- DotPattern component with orange dots and radial gradient
- File upload functionality in hero section
- Redirection to dashboard after successful upload
- Responsive design across all viewport sizes 